M|Plat|tx|\| Instagram (Fintech) \| Engagement rate \| 1.0–2.0% \|
M|Plat|tx|\| YouTube \| Avg view duration \| > 40% of vd length \|
M|Plat|tx|\| LinkedIn \| Post engagement rate \| 1–5% \|
