M|Anal|- Ev|noun + verb (e.g., `button_clicked`, `form_submitted`). Consistent across vt.
M|Anal|it|GA4 custom dimensions per vt. UTM all external links — no untagged traffic.
M|Anal|- **|tracking events w/o a decision attached — only instrument what will inform a choice.
M|A/B |it|One variable per tst. Define the sc metric before the tst starts — no post-hoc interpretation.
M|A/B |it|Minimum 2-week run or 500 conversions per variant — whichever comes first.
M|A/B |- **|stopping a tst early when results look promising — significance requires the full window.
M|SaaS|- Tr|MRR, ARR, MoM growth rate, NRR, churn rate, expansion MRR, contraction MRR.
M|SaaS|it|Cohort-based retention is more actionable than aggregate churn.
M|SaaS|- **|reporting MRR growth w/o separating new, expansion, contraction, and churn cp.
M|Busi|- Ru|growth, retention, margin, cash.
M|Busi|it|Flag any metric 20%+ below benchmark immediately — not at the end of the sn.
M|Busi|- **|presenting data w/o period-over-period context or benchmark comparison.